awscc_qbusiness_index (Data Source)

Data Source schema for AWS::QBusiness::Index

Schema

Read-Only

  • created_at (String)
  • description (String)
  • display_name (String)
  • document_attribute_configurations (Attributes List) (see below for nested schema)
  • index_arn (String)
  • index_id (String)
  • index_statistics (Attributes) (see below for nested schema)
  • status (String)
  • tags (Attributes List) (see below for nested schema)
  • type (String)
  • updated_at (String)
